Request Methods
c.BindJSON(obj interface{}): Binds JSON request body to the provided object.
c.BindXML(obj interface{}): Binds XML request body to the provided object.c.BindQuery(obj interface{}): Binds query parameters to the provided object.c.BindYAML(obj interface{}): Binds YAML request body to the provided object.c.BindHeader(obj interface{}): Binds request headers to the provided object.c.ShouldBind(obj interface{}): Automatically binds based on the Content-Type header.c.ShouldBindJSON(obj interface{}): Similar to BindJSON, but returns an error instead of aborting the request.c.ShouldBindQuery(obj interface{}): Similar to BindQuery, but returns an error instead of aborting the request.Response Methodsc.JSON(statusCode int, obj interface{}): Serializes the given struct as JSON into the response body.c.XML(statusCode int, obj interface{}): Serializes the given struct as XML into the response body.c.YAML(statusCode int, obj interface{}): Serializes the given struct as YAML into the response body.c.String(statusCode int, format string, values ...interface{}): Writes the formatted string into the response body.c.HTML(statusCode int, name string, obj interface{}): Renders an HTML template into the response body.c.Data(statusCode int, contentType string, data []byte): Writes raw data into the response body.c.File(filepath string): Sends a file as the response.c.Redirect(statusCode int, location string): Redirects the request to a new URL.c.Status(statusCode int): Sets the HTTP status code for the response.Parameter and Query Methodsc.Param(key string) string: Returns the value of the URL parameter.c.Query(key string) string: Returns the value of the query parameter.c.DefaultQuery(key, defaultValue string) string: Returns the value of the query parameter or the default value if the query parameter is not present.c.PostForm(key string) string: Returns the value of the form parameter.c.DefaultPostForm(key, defaultValue string) string: Returns the value of the form parameter or the default value if the form parameter is not present.c.GetHeader(key string) string: Returns the value of the request header.c.Cookie(name string) (string, error): Returns the value of the cookie.Context Control Methodsc.Abort(): Stops the remaining handlers from being executed.c.Next(): Executes the pending handlers in the chain.c.AbortWithStatus(statusCode int): Stops the remaining handlers and sets the status code.c.AbortWithStatusJSON(statusCode int, jsonObj interface{}): Stops the remaining handlers and sets the status code and JSON response.c.Set(key string, value interface{}): Stores a new key-value pair exclusively for this context.c.Get(key string) (value interface{}, exists bool): Retrieves a value from the context.c.MustGet(key string) interface{}: Retrieves a value from the context, panics if the value does not exist.Middleware Methodsc.IsAborted() bool: Returns whether the context is aborted.c.Errors: A collection of errors attached to the context.c.Error(err error): Attaches an error to the context.